<style>
  .about-section {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 120px 40px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .about-label {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8b0000;
    margin: 0;
    animation: slideDown 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes slideDown {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 115%;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0;
    animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out 0.1s both;
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .about-description {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 160%;
    color: #555555;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 700px;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .about-accent {
    color: #8b0000;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .about-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out 0.3s both;
  }

  .btn-learn-more {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: #8b0000;
    border: 2px solid #8b0000;
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-learn-more:hover {
    background-color: #8b0000;
    color: #ffffff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1199px) {
    .about-section {
      padding: 80px 40px;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 40px;
    }

    .about-description {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 809px) {
    .about-section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .about-container {
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 32px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .about-description {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 150%;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="about-section">
  <div class="about-container">
    <p class="about-label">Quiénes somos</p>

    <h2 class="about-title">
      Expertos en servicios técnicos con <span class="about-accent">garantía profesional</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="about-description">
      Desde nuestros inicios, Más de Chile ha proporcionado soluciones técnicas especializadas en hidrojet, gasfitería, cerrajería, obras civiles y emergencias 24/7. Con técnicos certificados, equipamiento de vanguardia y compromiso total con la calidad, hemos ganado la confianza de empresas y hogares en toda la Región Metropolitana durante años.
    </p>

    <div class="about-cta">
      <a href="#cotizar" class="btn-learn-more">
        Conocer nuestros servicios
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
